body.p: Registrere epoastačujuhusa vuostáiváldit ođasreivve ja dieđu go giinu cealká.

Sámi Siidda nuoraidprošeavtta Deanuleagi mánáid ja nuoraid kulturskuvla prošeakta oažžui davviriikkalaš ruhtadeami Davviriikkalaš kulturčuokkás (Nordisk kulturpoint). Ruhta lea juolluduvvon lágidit Deanuleagi nuoraid dáiddadáhpáhusa "Sápmi Talent".

-Mii leat hui ilus ja giitevaččat go searvi lea ožžon davviriikkalaš ruhtadeami Deanuleagi nuoraid dáiddadáhpáhussii. Dát ruhtadeapmi sihkkarastá dáhpáhusa lágideami, lohká prošeakta koordináhtor Annukka Hirvasvuopio-Laiti.

Dáiddadáhpáhus lágiduvvo Skábmadoaluid oktavuođas skábmamánus 2010 Ohcejotnjálmmis. Dáhpáhus lágiduvvo ovttasbarggus Deanu kulturskuvllain ja Issát Saba guovddážiin. Dáiddadáhpáhusa ulbmilin lea nanosmahtit sámenuoraid oktavuođaid rastá riikkarájáid ja addit báiki nuoraide čájehit dáidduideaset.

Ohcejoga gielddas ja maiddái Dáza beal´ Deanuleagis doaibmá "Deanuleagi Kulturskuvla-prošeakta" man ruhtáda Suoma Kulturruhtarádju. Prošeavtta ulbmilin lea lágidit nuoraide (13-17j.) davvisámegielat kulturfáláldagaid ja -oahpahusa. Prošeavtta hálddaša Sámi Siida -searvi, mii oaččui davviriikalaš Gollegiella-bálkkášumi jagis 2008. Bálkkášumi addojuvvui dan stuorra ja buorre barggu dihte, man searvi lea jo guhkes áiggi bargan sámegiela ovdaneami ja lunddolaš geavaheami ovdii. "Deanuleagi Kulturskuvla -prošeavttas" prošeaktakoordináhttorin bargá musihkkár, FM Annukka Hirvasvuopio-Laiti.

Hi, I am a big fan of Asian cuisine, and aohultgh they always contain loads of ingredients, when I want to forget about everyday life, I start cooking it, and the aromas and the preparation time turns my mind off. I especially like dishes that contain caviar. I loooove caviar. My favorite thing about it is its taste and the fact that it is so delicate yet so healthy. It contains loads of fatty acids, proteins and minerals that are very good for your blood vessels, heart and brain. I buy caviar online because I don"t trust supermarkets. It"s just my personal ideology thing. Thank you for this great recipe, and I am really happy for you for meeting Chef Bruce Lim!!

Thanks Susan and Greg for the updates. That is cltrainey disappointing to hear because I thought this plugin had a lot of potential. But with no support, it"s not worth it. If a plugin is going to be successful as a commercial offering, then it absolutely must have support. I"ve been busy is not a valid excuse. As a plugin developer myself, I understand it can be difficult to balance the need for support with the need for development, but as a consumer, I also expect at least a minimum level of service.Anyway, to reiterate to others what Susan and Greg have pointed out, there is a lack of support for this plugin, so I can"t recommend it. My suggestion to others is to look for an alternative commercial or free.
